reviews.text: Came for pizza a couple of nights ago...pizza not great.  Came today and got several appetizer plates....VERY good, but service is even better.  Young man working behind bar goes WAY above and beyond to give exemplary service...best I've had in some time.  Thank you Pizza Express...outstanding service, far beyond what's expected.   2/21 4pm.

Located near the wet market.  The floor area behind the bar was much larger.  Service was good.  Both English and Cantonese could be used.  Pizza and pasta were traditional.  Dessert was very sweet.  Price was moderate.  Many children during holiday and weekend.
tasty, fresh, healthy pasta(w/omni-pork) And extraordinary pizza
Nice atmosphere with wide variety of good italian foods and wine.   Highly recommended  for families with kids

Yo, wake up from your afternoon naps and handle customers! Usually avoid giant chains because of bland food, but at least the service is usually on point. Not here. I stood at the host stand and bar for 3 or 4 minutes, then finally walked up the stairs to the main dining room. Passed a “trainee” who pointed me to the manager sitting with another employee all the way in the back. No one even bothered to get up, so I left. WTH?!?

reviews.text:
This is a restaurant running with heart with a cute and unique cartoon character. ........   but, food itself is just soso....   which they need to improve significantly.

We have order chicken mustard sauce with rice as a set lunch, which tastes soooo plain.  Baked seafood fettuccine, better than the first one, squid is not bad, but needed to be waited for more than 20 minutes, which is very luxury for people who only have an hour for lunch.
Themed Cafe for Fluffyholics, note it is on 2nd floor of the building. Just push the door and inform the guard on duty that you will be visiting SOGNO CAFE
Great vibes and staffs. English speaking cafe in central. Specialty in desserts and chicken wings!
very cute and lovely cafe with limited seating. so come early/ make a reservation if you don't want to wait! Their most famous dessert is the rainbow cake, it's really fluffy and pretty.
Place for a nice lunch
